        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二童儿同上，诸葛亮上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兵扎祁山地，要擒司马懿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手捧地理图，报与丞相知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是。门上哪位在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "童儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "烦劳通禀：献图人求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "童儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "候着。\n启禀丞相：献图人求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "童儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "献图人，丞相传进。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，是。参见丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你奉何人所差？"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉王将军所差。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手捧何物？"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "地理图。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "展开。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮看图。旗牌欲下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "转来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快去到列柳城，调赵老将军回营！快去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，好一个胆大的马谡呀。临行之时，山人怎样吩咐与你：叫你靠山近水，安\n营扎寨。怎么你不听我言，偏偏在山顶扎寨？只恐街亭难保。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀丞相：马谡失守街亭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如何，果然把街亭失守了。虽然马谡失守街亭，乃是我诸葛亮之罪也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "司马懿带兵复夺西城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然，司马带兵复夺西城。哎，想先帝在白帝城托孤之时，言道：马谡言过其\n实，终无大用。悔不听先帝之言，错用马谡，失守街亭，我是悔之晚矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "司马懿大兵离西城还有四十余里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，司马懿的大兵，他来得好快呀！哽，他来得好快呀！人道司马用兵如神，\n今日一见，是令人可服，令人可敬。\n哎呀，且住。说什么令人可服，令人可敬？想这西城的兵将，俱被山人调遣在\n外，司马懿大兵到此，难道叫我军束手就擒，这束手就擒！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（童儿允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传老军们进见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "童儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传老军们进见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二老军同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哽唬！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军甲",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "司马兵到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军乙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心惊肉跳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤小人们进帐，有何差遣？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们可是西城的老军？"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你等将西城四门大开，打扫街道。司马懿大兵到此，不要害怕，违令者斩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军甲",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相吩咐我，"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军乙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "准死不能活。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二老军下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "琴童，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（童儿允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带定瑶琴美酒，随山人敌楼去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "童儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天呀，天哪！汉室兴败就在我这空城一计也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我用兵数十年从来谨慎，\n悔不该差马谡无用之人。\n望空中求先帝要大显神灵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮下。）"
        }
      ],
