    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "一来是马谡无谋少学问",
        "二老军",
        "众人",
        "你休要胡思乱想心不定",
        "你的计策休瞒我",
        "司马懿",
        "司马昭",
        "左右琴童人两个",
        "左右琴童来捧酒",
        "我也曾命人去打听",
        "我本当传将令杀进城",
        "旌旗招展空翻影",
        "有人若把西城进",
        "老军乙",
        "老军甲",
        "诸葛亮",
        "诸葛亮在城楼把驾等",
        "赵云",
        "进得城来无别敬",
        "连得我三城多侥幸"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二老军同上，打扫街道。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二童儿引诸葛亮同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那马谡失街亭令人可恨，\n这时候倒叫我难以调停。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，司马懿大兵到此，丞相不遣将对敌，反将四门大开，是何原故呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我倒明白了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你明白什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相有点老糊涂呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老军们因何故你们纷纷议论？"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是小人们纷纷议论，司马懿大兵到此，不遣将对敌，反将四门大开，是何原\n故？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "国家事用不着尔等当心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "话虽如此，国家事不用小人们当心。西城到汉中，乃是咽喉路径，司马大兵到\n来，一拥而进，西城失守，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "从西城到汉中乃是咽喉路径，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔来看，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我城内早埋伏有十万神兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，伙计，怪不得丞相不着急，城里头埋伏好的十万神兵呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我倒不信，我去看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老军乙看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看见没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "认什么，无有看见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你肉眼凡胎，看不见的，让我去看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老军甲看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军甲",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看见没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要说人，连个鬼影子都没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "劝你们放大了胆把街道扫净，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（后场擂鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "退司马保空城全仗此琴。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮上城。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "司马懿 （内西皮导板） 得了街亭望西城，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、司马懿、司马师、司马昭同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马懿",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "城门大开为何因？"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马懿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，适才探马报道：西城乃是空城。老夫兴兵到此，为何四门大开。咦，你\n看诸葛亮又在那里弄鬼，不要中了他人之计，待我先传一令。众将官，听我令\n下："
        },
        {
          "character": "司马懿",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "坐在马上传一令，\n大小将官听分明：\n定斩首级不容情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "有人若把西城进、众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我本是卧龙岗散淡的人，\n论阴阳如反掌保定乾坤。\n算就了汉家业鼎足三分。\n东西征南北剿博古通今。\n诸葛亮怎比得前辈的先生。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮抚琴。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我面前缺少个知音的人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马懿",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "坐在马上来观定，\n城楼上坐的是诸葛孔明。\n打扫街道老弱残兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "左右琴童来捧酒、我本当传将令杀进城、众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喝！"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马懿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马懿",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又恐怕中了他巧计行。\n棋逢敌手一样人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "你的计策休瞒我、诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我正在城楼观山景，\n耳听得城外乱纷纷。\n却原来是司马发来的兵。\n打听那司马领兵往西行。\n二来是将帅不和，失守我的街亭。\n贪而无厌又夺我的西城。\n等候你司马到此，咱们谈、谈、谈谈心。\n我只有羊羔美酒，美酒羊羔，犒赏你的三军。\n又无有埋伏又无有兵。\n你就来、来、来，请上城楼，司马你听我扶琴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旌旗招展空翻影、我也曾命人去打听、一来是马谡无谋少学问、连得我三城多侥幸、诸葛亮在城楼把驾等、进得城来无别敬、左右琴童人两个、你休要胡思乱想心不定、司马懿",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "左思右想心不定，\n城内必有埋伏兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听他琴内慌迫，一定是空城。乘此机会，杀进城去……"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马懿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哽。那孔明平生谨慎，从不弄险，不要中了他人之计。将前队改为后队，人马\n倒退四十余里。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（龙套欲下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马懿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我说破于他。\n诸葛亮呀，诸葛孔明，你实城也罢，空城也罢，你司马老爷是不进城了。请呀\n请呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（龙套、司马懿同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀丞相：司马懿人马倒退四十余里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二老军同下，诸葛亮下城。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人言司马有才能，\n带兵不敢进西城。\n等马谡回营来以正军情。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手、赵云同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，老将军呀。今有司马带兵夺取西城，被山人略施小计，他兵退四十里。\n恐他复夺西城，老将军快快抵挡一阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵云引四上手下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎豹归山禽兽远，蛟龙得水快如沧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮下。）"
        }
      ],
