    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "司马懿",
        "司马昭"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、司马懿、司马师、司马昭同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马懿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸呸！我说是实城，你们说是空城。那赵云从天上掉下来的不成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等哪里知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "司马懿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "诸葛亮呀，你的胆也太大了！司马懿呀，你的胆也就太小了！看将起来，司马"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
